lead_paragraph: Trying to serve out the biggest victory of her career, 18-year-old Ana Konjuh was startled — right along with everyone else under the roof in Arthur Ashe Stadium — by a piercing noise coming from the U.S. Open arena's sound system during a ball toss.

headline.print_headline: Konjuh, 18, in 1st Slam QF After Upsetting Radwanska at Open
headline.main: Konjuh, 18, in 1st Slam QF After Upsetting Radwanska at Open
